Interface Signed

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, CompiledAction, CompiledFluent, CompiledTrigger, Fluent, PrefixFluent, Trigger
public interface Signed extends Logical
An interface for anything which has a Signature. This class overrides Logical.compareTo(Logical) so that two signed objects will be compared using their signatures.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
